HEADWORD: Mumblety peg
<hw>Mum"ble*ty peg`</hw></mhw>
<pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A game played with a pocketknife, the
object of which is to throw the knife in any of a vairety of ways (such
as over the back), or from various positions, and have it stick in the
ground or another surface. Also called <altname>mumble-the-peg</altname>
and <altname>mumble peg</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Mumblenews</ent>⟦br⟧
